biography.content:
Completed 2 years as an undergraduate at the University of Alberta in the Faculty of Science
Completed 2 years in the Bachelor of Science with specialization in Genetics
Attending Medicine school in September 2014 at National University of Ireland (5-year program)

As of 2014 I have started working as an undergraduate research student at the University of Alberta, and will continue over the years/summer on different projects with my supervisor and other research students.
